{"tid":1557273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳恆大教師戴頭盔口罩上課","createTime":"2019-09-10T04:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T10:05:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3ccd9739f41948ba691a30171d00d356b2c77998","tid":1557273,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:50:48.000Z","msg":"反送中引發的香港街頭示威衝突持續不斷，近日網路流傳一張疑似香港恆生大學教師上課時，身穿全副裝備，聲援反送中示威的照片。<br />\n<br />\n星島網報導，網友Caidy Ng上傳的照片中，該名教師身穿黑衣，戴上黃色頭盔和「豬嘴」口罩上課，疑似聲援反送中的示威者。恆生大學回應表示，非常關注有關事件，正在了解當中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/09/10/realtime/6802193.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F09%2F10%2Frealtime%2F6802193.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600%26exp%3D3600&h=637c07e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該名教師身穿黑衣，戴上頭盔和「豬嘴」口罩上課。圖：取自星島日報網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/4039120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5603%2F4039120&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=d4f64a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/4039120</a>"},{"pid":"797e5b635306328a1abc14408cfa08c73212df45","tid":1557273,"uid":29594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07993bee36890b0f46a8d419d71e5f017c177cfc","tid":1557273,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a hr